{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "strings": {
    "All locally cached thumbnails will be deleted and re-fetched as you browse.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ローカルにキャッシュ済みのサムネイルはすべて削除され、閲覧時に再取得されます。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Auto (%lld MB)": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "自動（%lld MB）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Cancel": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "キャンセル"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Clear": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "消去"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Clear Photo Cache": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "写真キャッシュを消去"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Clear Photo Cache?": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "写真キャッシュを消去しますか？"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Disk limit": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ディスク上限"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Disk usage": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ディスク使用量"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Library": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ライブラリ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Memory limit": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "メモリ上限"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Photo Cache": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "写真キャッシュ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Photos": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "写真"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Stores already-decoded, cell-sized thumbnails so the grid scrolls smoothly without re-decoding each photo (and without re-fetching iCloud-optimized originals). Full photos are never duplicated here — only small thumbnails. “Auto” scales the memory limit to this device's RAM.": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "デコード済みのセルサイズのサムネイルを保存し、写真を再デコードせず（iCloud 最適化された元画像も再取得せず）グリッドを滑らかにスクロールできます。フル画像はここに重複保存されません（小さなサムネイルのみ）。「自動」は端末の RAM に応じてメモリ上限を調整します。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "User albums": {
      "localizations": {
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "ユーザーアルバム"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version": "1.0"
}
